name: Infinity ∞ Fly
description: Infinity is not a real number, it is an idea. An idea of something without an end.  Infinity cannot be measured.  Even these faraway galaxies can't compete with infinity.We can sometimes use infinity like it is a number, but infinity does not behave like a real number.  Example: ∞ + 1 = ∞ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ Handcrafted frame by frame animation, Original Sound Design & Mixed Media //////////////////// /twitter.com/jvyvazquez ∞ instagram.com/jvyvazquez
